WEBVTT

00:01.067 --> 00:03.235
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:03.237 --> 00:04.736
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da ♪
Let's go!

00:04.738 --> 00:06.438
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:06.440 --> 00:09.107
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:09.109 --> 00:11.342
♪ Yeah, we'll be there ♪

00:11.344 --> 00:13.412
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:13.414 --> 00:15.747
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:15.749 --> 00:17.081
♪ We'll jump out the bush ♪

00:17.083 --> 00:18.784
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:18.786 --> 00:20.219
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:30.197 --> 00:32.297
[ Vacuum cleaner running ]

00:32.299 --> 00:33.966
Sorry, Miki-Chan.

00:42.476 --> 00:45.310
[<i> Video game beeping</i> ]

00:45.312 --> 00:47.479
[ Gasps ] You guys!
Look at this mess!

00:47.481 --> 00:48.947
This place looks gross.
Ugh!

00:48.949 --> 00:51.149
-Blocking the TV, dude.
-[ Groans ]

00:51.151 --> 00:53.451
Huh? Grizz,
peanut butter again?

00:53.453 --> 00:55.153
Ugh, you can't just
leave this out.

00:55.155 --> 00:56.755
You know I'm allergic.

00:56.757 --> 00:58.791
[ Laughs ]
Eat fireballs, bro.

00:58.793 --> 01:00.492
Bigger fireball.
[<i> Explosion</i> ]

01:00.494 --> 01:02.160
Dang, you're good.

01:02.162 --> 01:03.562
Mike drop.

01:03.564 --> 01:05.096
Ugh, seriously, guys?

01:05.098 --> 01:08.000
I mean, could you at least try
and clean up after yourselves?

01:08.002 --> 01:10.335
-What's got you all worked up?
-Nothing, nothing.

01:10.337 --> 01:12.337
I just think this place
could be cleaner, you know.

01:12.339 --> 01:15.006
Ooh, I know what it is.

01:15.008 --> 01:16.174
Fruit Friday.

01:16.176 --> 01:18.510
Fruit Friday, Pando-Wando.

01:18.512 --> 01:20.245
Uh, what --
Oh, is it Friday?

01:20.247 --> 01:21.679
I had no idea.

01:21.681 --> 01:22.781
[ Knock on door ]
[ Gasps ]

01:22.783 --> 01:24.483
Ugh. Whoa!
[ Chuckles ]

01:24.485 --> 01:27.185
Hiya, bears!
Happy Fruit Friday!

01:27.187 --> 01:28.420
-Hey, girl.
-'Sup?

01:28.422 --> 01:30.188
Hi, Lucy! Whoa.
[ Clears Throat ]

01:30.190 --> 01:31.522
[ Deep voice ]
Hello, Lucy.

01:31.524 --> 01:33.191
Whoa, here we go.
Let me help you with that.

01:33.193 --> 01:34.626
Ooh, careful.
It's a bit heavy.

01:34.628 --> 01:37.829
[ Groans ] Yeah, no, not to me.
I'm good. It's fine.

01:37.831 --> 01:40.531
So, how are my favorite
customers today?

01:40.533 --> 01:42.367
Ice Bear is excited
for many fruits.

01:42.369 --> 01:44.002
Well, I got
- all of your favorites.

01:44.004 --> 01:45.537
Pink Ladies for Grizz.

01:45.539 --> 01:46.838
Ooh!
My ladies.

01:46.840 --> 01:49.774
And for you,
- one extra large eggplant.

01:49.776 --> 01:50.608
Catch!

01:50.610 --> 01:52.143
Mm.
[ Kisses ]

01:52.145 --> 01:53.711
[ Grunts ]
Uh, hey, Lucy,

01:53.713 --> 01:55.780
do you want to stick around
for some iced tea?

01:55.782 --> 01:57.048
Aww, I'd love to,

01:57.050 --> 01:59.618
but I'm already way behind
on my deliveries today.

01:59.620 --> 02:01.386
-[ Coughs ]
-Clifford!

02:01.388 --> 02:02.720
[ Breathing heavily ]

02:02.722 --> 02:04.456
I told you to stay
in the car, buddy.

02:04.458 --> 02:06.458
You're allergic
to, like, everything outside.

02:06.460 --> 02:08.626
I don't want to be
in the car anymore.

02:08.628 --> 02:11.797
You promised we'd watch
"Robot Laser Rangers."

02:11.799 --> 02:14.132
I know,
but I have to work today.

02:14.134 --> 02:15.700
Hey-hey,
who's this little guy?

02:15.702 --> 02:18.036
Oh, this is my little brother,
Clifford.

02:18.038 --> 02:19.404
Say hi, Cliff.

02:19.406 --> 02:21.072
[ Coughs ]

02:21.074 --> 02:22.307
I'm watching him today,

02:22.309 --> 02:24.075
but I still have
tons of deliveries to do.

02:24.077 --> 02:27.245
Ugh, my little bud's not having
any fun with his big sis.

02:27.247 --> 02:28.580
Oh, bummer.

02:28.582 --> 02:30.549
Wish we could do something
to help out.

02:30.551 --> 02:32.083
[ Thinking ]
<i>Wait a minute.</i>

02:32.085 --> 02:35.853
<i>If I look after Clifford,</i>
<i>therefore helping Lucy,</i>

02:35.855 --> 02:39.091
<i>then she'll see how responsible</i>
<i>I am and fall in love with me,</i>

02:39.093 --> 02:41.726
<i>and we'll get married</i>
<i>and be together forever.</i>

02:41.728 --> 02:43.595
[<i> Laughs</i> ]
<i>Oh, okay, you know, be cool.</i>

02:43.597 --> 02:45.096
<i>You got this.</i>

02:45.098 --> 02:48.033
Uh, hey, Lucy! Uh, how about
I hang out with Clifford

02:48.035 --> 02:51.069
so that you can finish
your deliveries on time?

02:51.071 --> 02:53.371
Really?
Ooh, um, ugh,

02:53.373 --> 02:56.407
I don't know.
- Cliff can be a bit of a handful.

02:56.409 --> 02:58.043
-[ Chuckles ]
-I'm high maintenance.

02:58.045 --> 03:01.046
Ha! So's my baby bro. They'll
be perfect for one another.

03:01.048 --> 03:02.914
Oh, and we can help you
finish your deliveries.

03:02.916 --> 03:04.949
-Wait, what?
-Well, yeah.

03:04.951 --> 03:06.785
I mean,
that would be amazing!

03:06.787 --> 03:08.620
-Are you guys sure?
-Of course!

03:08.622 --> 03:10.455
Whoo-hoo!
I call shotgun!

03:10.457 --> 03:12.224
-[ Laughs ]
-Ice Bear's bringing eggplant.

03:12.226 --> 03:15.694
[ Laughs nervously ]
Well, I guess this is happening.

03:15.696 --> 03:17.796
Okay, so here is
his emergency backpack

03:17.798 --> 03:19.797
with all his
allergy stuff inside.

03:19.799 --> 03:23.535
Oh, thanks, Panda. You're
really helping me out today.

03:23.537 --> 03:25.037
[ Giggles ]

03:25.039 --> 03:27.572
Be good to Panda and call me
if you need anything.

03:27.574 --> 03:29.307
Bye, guys! Have fun!

03:29.309 --> 03:30.809
[ Engine starts ]
Bye, Lucy!

03:30.811 --> 03:34.646
Your little bud
is in good hands!

03:34.648 --> 03:36.814
Okay, Clifford, le--

03:36.816 --> 03:39.418
Uh, Clifford?
W-Where are you, little guy?

03:39.420 --> 03:41.219
Th-This isn't funny.

03:41.221 --> 03:43.221
Clifford? Come on out!

03:43.223 --> 03:44.489
Please.

03:44.491 --> 03:45.890
Clifford!

03:45.892 --> 03:47.158
Clifford.
[ Sighs ]

03:47.160 --> 03:50.228
What are you doing
just sitting in the tub?

03:50.230 --> 03:52.630
[ Sniffs ]
I like the tub.

03:52.632 --> 03:54.432
It's cold in here.

03:54.434 --> 03:56.401
Uh, sure.

03:56.403 --> 03:58.803
Um, do you want to play tag
or something?

03:58.805 --> 04:01.439
Kids like tag, right?
That's a thing.

04:01.441 --> 04:03.308
I guess.

04:03.310 --> 04:04.509
Um, okay.

04:04.511 --> 04:06.644
Tag. You're it.

04:06.646 --> 04:08.180
You're supposed
to chase me.

04:08.182 --> 04:10.682
Oh.

04:10.684 --> 04:12.117
[ Breathing heavily ]

04:12.119 --> 04:15.086
Aah!
W-W-What do you need?

04:15.088 --> 04:16.854
-Inhaler.
-Oh!

04:16.856 --> 04:18.690
[ Inhaler hisses ]
[ Inhales deeply ]

04:18.692 --> 04:19.925
[ Chuckles nervously ]

04:19.927 --> 04:22.461
Let's do something
less active.

04:25.799 --> 04:27.966
Oh, shoot!
[ Tires squeal ]

04:27.968 --> 04:30.435
Oh, where's my head?
I totally forgot to tell Panda

04:30.437 --> 04:31.769
about the extra allergy pen.

04:31.771 --> 04:33.704
Whoa, Lucy, what's up?
Why so stressed?

04:33.706 --> 04:35.707
Oh, I just get so worried
about Clifford.

04:35.709 --> 04:37.008
He's so sensitive.

04:37.010 --> 04:39.177
Easy, Lucy.
He's safe with Pan-Man.

04:39.179 --> 04:40.879
Trust me. He'll be fine.

04:40.881 --> 04:44.182
So just relax with us and
stay loosey, Lucy. [ Laughs ]

04:44.184 --> 04:45.884
We'll get your deliveries done
in no time.

04:45.886 --> 04:48.386
Now, first thing's first.
Hand over the phone.

04:48.388 --> 04:50.055
[ Sighs ]
Okay. I can do this.

04:50.057 --> 04:51.222
Loosey Lucy.

04:51.224 --> 04:54.025
Great. Second thing --
Some soothing music.

04:54.027 --> 04:56.494
[ Heavy metal music playing ]
♪ Bang your head to the boogie ♪

04:56.496 --> 04:57.896
♪ To the beat now, bang ♪

04:59.533 --> 05:02.200
Hmm. We have a lot
of the same allergies.

05:02.202 --> 05:03.735
Hmm. Pickles?

05:03.737 --> 05:05.737
-No.
-Okay, then.

05:05.739 --> 05:08.073
[ Muttering ]
Can he do potato chips?

05:08.075 --> 05:09.741
Oh, gluten. No.

05:09.743 --> 05:12.343
Peanut butter?
Nope. No way.

05:12.345 --> 05:14.045
Well, it looks like
the only thing you can eat

05:14.047 --> 05:16.981
is this can of olives.
How about it?

05:16.983 --> 05:18.516
W-Wait, what are you doing?

05:18.518 --> 05:20.819
My doctor said
I should lie like this.

05:20.821 --> 05:22.921
Um, okay, you do that.

05:22.923 --> 05:25.423
I'll go get us a bowl, okay?

05:25.425 --> 05:27.325
[ Coughs ]

05:27.327 --> 05:30.328
All right, one bowl of olives
coming right --

05:30.330 --> 05:32.230
Oh, not again!

05:32.232 --> 05:34.265
C-Clifford? Clif-Clifford?

05:34.267 --> 05:36.768
Come on, Clifford.
This isn't funny anymore.

05:36.770 --> 05:38.770
[ Muffled cough ]

05:38.772 --> 05:41.773
Hey, Cliff, I got a big bowl
of yummy, olivey goodness here.

05:41.775 --> 05:44.042
Come on, buddy.

05:44.044 --> 05:46.278
[ Sighs ] Look, I know
that allergies are a bummer,

05:46.280 --> 05:48.846
but sometimes good things
can come out of it,

05:48.848 --> 05:51.115
like I never would have --
have met your sister

05:51.117 --> 05:52.417
without my peanut allergy,

05:52.419 --> 05:55.187
and -- and then I wouldn't have
become friends with you.

05:55.189 --> 05:56.954
We're friends?

05:56.956 --> 06:00.424
Yeah, of course
we're friends.

06:00.426 --> 06:02.527
Can I have an olive?

06:07.200 --> 06:09.101
[ Coughs ]

06:13.640 --> 06:15.207
These go
to the fruit department.

06:15.209 --> 06:17.609
Well, there's only one way
to move this much fruit.

06:17.611 --> 06:19.910
-An assembly line?
-Nope, a conga line!

06:19.912 --> 06:22.981
♪ Dance in the line,
sway to the side ♪

06:22.983 --> 06:24.649
[ Laughs ]
♪ Dance in the line ♪

06:24.651 --> 06:26.318
♪ Sway to the side ♪

06:26.320 --> 06:29.787
♪ Jump in the sound,
we moving all around, ja rah ♪

06:29.789 --> 06:31.589
♪ What a chilly day ♪

06:31.591 --> 06:32.991
[ Both laughing ]

06:32.993 --> 06:35.326
♪ Nice to have friends
on a Saturday ♪

06:35.328 --> 06:39.163
♪ Gonna take my time
to hang here with my crew ♪

06:39.165 --> 06:42.734
♪ Nice to have friends
on a Saturday ♪

06:42.736 --> 06:44.068
Whoo!
- ♪ They stare, don't care ♪

06:44.070 --> 06:45.470
[ Whistling ]
♪ That's how we walk ♪

06:45.472 --> 06:48.840
♪ Nice to have friends
on a Saturday ♪

06:48.842 --> 06:52.076
♪ So casual as we cruise
around the block ♪

06:52.078 --> 06:55.012
♪ Wasn't that nice to have
friends on a Saturday ♪

06:55.014 --> 06:58.349
♪ Dance in the line,
sway to the side ♪

06:58.351 --> 06:59.651
♪ Dance in the line ♪

06:59.653 --> 07:01.152
[ Laughter ]
♪ Sway to the side ♪

07:01.154 --> 07:02.753
Whoo! [ Laughs ]
♪ I say, dance in the line ♪

07:02.755 --> 07:05.290
[ Both panting ]
♪ Sway to the side ♪

07:05.292 --> 07:07.192
[ Inhalers hiss ]
♪ Movin' all around ♪

07:07.194 --> 07:08.660
[ Both laugh ]

07:10.364 --> 07:12.997
That's the last of it. Thank you
guys for all your help.

07:12.999 --> 07:14.866
-No probs, girl.
-Ice Bear enjoyed employment.

07:14.868 --> 07:16.200
Oh, hey,
now you can text Pan-Pan

07:16.202 --> 07:18.136
and let him know
we're on our way home.

07:18.138 --> 07:19.204
Great!

07:19.206 --> 07:20.838
[ Both laugh ]

07:20.840 --> 07:23.207
Okay, okay, now we got
to take a selfie.

07:23.209 --> 07:25.877
-[ Laughs ]
-You really want one with me?

07:25.879 --> 07:28.813
Usually it's only Lucy
who takes selfies with me.

07:28.815 --> 07:30.881
Well, not anymore!
Get in here.

07:30.883 --> 07:33.117
[ Laughs ]
Okay, smile!

07:33.119 --> 07:34.819
[ Cellphone chirps, vibrates ]

07:34.821 --> 07:36.554
-What?
-J-Just ignore that.

07:36.556 --> 07:37.722
-That's nothing.
-Give it!

07:37.724 --> 07:40.324
-No, wait!
-"Future Mrs. Panda"?

07:40.326 --> 07:41.726
No, don't tell Lucy.

07:41.728 --> 07:43.828
Wait, Clifford,
you don't understand!

07:43.830 --> 07:46.064
Clifford, uh,
it's not what you think.

07:46.066 --> 07:48.366
-I can explain.
-You were only using me

07:48.368 --> 07:51.669
to get close to Lucy,
just like all the others.

07:51.671 --> 07:54.239
No, Clifford, I --
Wait, there are others?

07:54.241 --> 07:56.007
-Wait, wha-- wha--
-I hate you, Panda!

07:56.009 --> 07:58.509
No, don't run!
You'll hyperventilate!

07:58.511 --> 07:59.677
[ Splat ]
[ Grunts ]

07:59.679 --> 08:03.248
Oh, geez. Aah.
Are you okay?

08:03.250 --> 08:05.650
Oh, peanut butter!
He's gonna die!

08:05.652 --> 08:07.385
That's weird.
Still no reply.

08:07.387 --> 08:09.187
But Panda never
misses your texts.

08:09.189 --> 08:10.588
I know.
We got to get home.

08:10.590 --> 08:12.023
-Keep texting.
-Okay, but --

08:12.025 --> 08:14.358
Aah!
[ Tires squeal ]

08:14.360 --> 08:16.760
[ Panting ]

08:16.762 --> 08:19.530
[ Cellphone chiming, vibrating ]

08:19.532 --> 08:21.700
Aah, no, no,
no, no, not now!

08:21.702 --> 08:23.601
Aah, where is that
emergency bag?

08:23.603 --> 08:25.569
[ Grunting ]

08:25.571 --> 08:27.405
Allergy pen. Allergy pen!

08:27.407 --> 08:28.906
Oh, come on. Where is it?

08:28.908 --> 08:30.342
Where is it?

08:30.344 --> 08:31.609
Oh, the kitchen!

08:31.611 --> 08:32.944
[ Panting ]

08:32.946 --> 08:35.280
[ Gasps ]
The backpack!

08:35.282 --> 08:36.347
Ugh.

08:36.349 --> 08:40.451
[ Distorted ]
Oh, no. Peanut butter!

08:40.453 --> 08:41.552
Dang it.

08:41.554 --> 08:43.221
[ Thud ]

08:43.223 --> 08:44.455
[ Groaning ]

08:44.457 --> 08:46.390
[ Grunting ]

08:46.392 --> 08:48.793
[ Mumbling ]

08:48.795 --> 08:50.294
Backpack.

08:50.296 --> 08:52.430
[ Grunting ]

08:55.301 --> 08:56.935
Backpack!

08:59.205 --> 09:00.571
[ Thud ]

09:00.573 --> 09:03.308
[ Continues mumbling ]

09:10.650 --> 09:11.916
Clifford.

09:11.918 --> 09:14.119
I'm coming, Clifford!

09:16.489 --> 09:19.490
[ Wheezing ]

09:19.492 --> 09:21.426
Hold on, Clifford!

09:23.663 --> 09:25.497
[ Breathing heavily ]

09:27.500 --> 09:29.668
Clifford, I'm so sorry.

09:29.670 --> 09:32.336
At first, I was using you
to get close to Lucy,

09:32.338 --> 09:35.973
but then -- then I really did
think of you as a friend.

09:35.975 --> 09:38.176
Please forgive me.

09:43.015 --> 09:46.584
That's fair.
- I deserve to perish alone.

09:46.586 --> 09:49.120
Goodbye.

09:49.122 --> 09:52.190
[ Thud ]
[ Gasps ]

09:52.192 --> 09:53.792
You alive?

09:53.794 --> 09:55.793
I am, but how?

09:55.795 --> 09:58.964
Lucy always packs
a spare allergy pen.

10:01.702 --> 10:03.434
[ Tires squeal ]

10:03.436 --> 10:05.537
Oh, my gosh. Oh, my gosh.
Clifford, Clifford,

10:05.539 --> 10:08.506
are you o...kay?

10:08.508 --> 10:10.375
Oh, hey, guys.
Sorry we missed your texts.

10:10.377 --> 10:12.010
We were just super
into this episode

10:12.012 --> 10:15.280
of "Laser Robot Rangers."
Surprisingly good show.

10:15.282 --> 10:17.782
[ Sighs ] I guess I didn't need
to worry so much.

10:17.784 --> 10:19.217
Ah, you did great, Lucy.

10:19.219 --> 10:21.385
Ice Bear thought
you were chill. Enough.

10:21.387 --> 10:23.621
Phew, eating all that fruit
made me hungry.

10:23.623 --> 10:25.556
-Let's eat.
-[ Laughs ]

10:25.558 --> 10:29.794
Cliffy! Aww, I missed
my little partner in crime.

10:29.796 --> 10:31.963
[ Groans ]
Too tight, Lucy.

10:31.965 --> 10:34.031
Can I hang out with Panda
again sometime?

10:34.033 --> 10:36.568
Uh, yeah, if Panda
is okay with it.

10:36.570 --> 10:40.038
Of course, but as his friend,
not as his babysitter.

10:40.040 --> 10:41.239
Yeah!
[ Coughs ]

10:41.241 --> 10:42.874
Hey, whoa,
easy there, Clifford.

10:42.876 --> 10:44.241
Go get your stuff, okay?

10:44.243 --> 10:46.544
-See you, buddy!
-Bye, Panda.

10:46.546 --> 10:49.080
You know, he doesn't really
take to people much.

10:49.082 --> 10:51.248
You must have made
an impression on him.

10:51.250 --> 10:54.018
[ Chuckling ]
Well, you know, I --

10:54.020 --> 10:55.419
Thank you, Panda.
[ Kisses ]

10:55.421 --> 10:57.588
See you next Friday!

10:57.590 --> 10:59.723
[ Panting ]

10:59.725 --> 11:02.360
[ Inhaler hisses ]

11:03.897 --> 11:06.898
♪♪
